Euro-Area Leaders to Hold Summit in Brussels on Oct. 18

-- B y   J a m e s   G .   N e u g e r
-- 
2011-10-06T07:03:32Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-06/euro-area-leaders-to-hold-summit-in-brussels-on-oct-18.html
Euro-area government leaders will
meet Oct. 18 in Brussels, the day after the next scheduled
European Union summit, the EU said.  The summit of all 27 EU leaders was condensed into one day,
Oct. 17, to free up time for the euro-area meeting, an EU
spokesman said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James G. Neuger at 
 jneuger@bloomberg.net  